Definition: the sacred writings of the Christian religions
Example: he went to carry the Word to the heathen
Synonyms: adj, pert, biblical, Christian_Bible, Book, Good_Book, Holy_Scripture, Holy_Writ, Scripture, scriptural, Word_of_God, Word, sacred_text, the, sacred, writings, of, Christian, religions, he, went, to, carry, heathen
Category: noun.communication
